    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv Thanks for your response!  \r\n\r\nAt first, I wasn't sure what you meant by `facetOrdering`, so I searched for it but couldn’t find much information. Eventually, I stumbled upon the settings in the \"back office\" under **Configuration → Filtering and Faceting → Facet Display**.  \r\n\r\nIt wasn’t immediately clear to me that I needed to add facets there as well. Thanks for pointing me in the right direction!  \r\n",
